### MFA API Testing
### این فایل برای تست MFA endpoints استفاده می‌شه

### 1. ابتدا Login کنید تا Access Token بگیرید
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test123!@#",
  "rememberMe": false
}

### 2. MFA Methods را دریافت کنید
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/mfa
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3. MFA Status را بررسی کنید
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/mfa/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 4. TOTP MFA Setup
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/mfa/setup
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": 0,
  "phoneNumber": null
}

### 5. SMS MFA Setup
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/mfa/setup
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": 1,
  "phoneNumber": "+989123456789"
}

### 6. Backup Codes MFA Setup
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/mfa/setup
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": 2,
  "phoneNumber": null
}

### 7. TOTP MFA Verify
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/mfa/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": 0,
  "code": "123456",
  "rememberDevice": false
}

### 8. SMS MFA Verify
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/mfa/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": 1,
  "code": "123456",
  "rememberDevice": true
}

### 9. Backup Codes MFA Verify
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/mfa/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": 2,
  "code": "ABC12345",
  "rememberDevice": false
}

### 10. MFA Disable
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/mfa/disable
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": 0
}

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5187
@accessToken = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE 